author: wtopstaff
title: Presidents Cup Results
text:
By The Associated Press October 10, 2015 12:04 am Saturday At Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea Incheon, South Korea UNITED STATES 7½, INTERNATIONAL 6½ Foursomes United States 2, International 2 
Louis Oosthuizen and Branden Grace, International, def. Patrick Reed and Rickie Fowler, United States, 3 and 2. 
Bubba Watson and J.B. Holmes, United States, halved with Adam Scott and Marc Leishman, International. 
Bill Haas and Matt Kuchar, United States, halved with Sang-moon Bae and Hideki Matsuyama, International. 
Dustin Johnson and Jordan Spieth, United States, def. Jason Day and Charl Schwartzel, International, 1 up. Topics:
